Ionotropic:
- AMPA: LGIC for Ca2+, Na+, K+
- Kainate: LGIC for Na+, K+, (presynaptic: -, postsynaptic: +)
- NMDA: LGIC, non-selective to cations

Metabotropic: (mGluRn with n in [brackets])
- Group I [1,5]: Class C, Gq coupled (+)
- Group II [2,3]: Class C, Gi/G0 coupled (-)
- Group III [4,6,7,8]: Class C, Gi/G0 coupled (-)
